      "id": "53daf005",
      "status": "draft",
      "scope": "cross-domain",
      "title": "Implement Qoder provider with both PAT and OAuth support in AxonRouter-GO",
      "rationale": "User confirmed Qoder must support both personal access token (PAT, current pt-* path via qodercli) and OAuth authorization-code flow. OmniRoute will be the primary reference; 9router's deprecated COSY/WAF signing path will not be ported.",
      "consequences": "Adds OAuth service skeleton, updates executor to route PAT vs OAuth/apikey tokens, updates provider catalog category to oauth with dual-mode UI, adds PAT import and quota fetcher, and adds tests.",
